				Devour.com | Awesome Hand-Picked Videos
			</a>
			<a href="#" class="topsite">
				MacRumors: Apple Mac iOS Rumors
			</a>
			<a href="#" class="topsite">
				Tumblr
			</a>
			<a href="#" class="topsite">
				reddit: the front page of the internet
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="meta">
		<a href="http://github.com/scottjacksonx/strt">strt v<%= version %></a>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
